PhysicalTable.name: SAMP_REVENUE_F
PhysicalTable.Description: Reveue Fact table: Stores the fact information at the lowest grain.

PhysicalColumn.name: Bill_Qtr_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Bill Quarter Key: Joins to Qtr_Key of Time dimension table (Qtr grain).

PhysicalColumn.name: Cust_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Customer Key: Joins to Cust_Key column of Customers dimension table.

PhysicalColumn.name: Revenue
PhysicalColumn.Description: Revenue: Stores revenue information as a double.

PhysicalColumn.name: Order_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Order Number: Uniquely identifies each record in the fact table.

PhysicalColumn.name: Bill_Day_Dt
PhysicalColumn.Description: Bill Day Date: Joins to Calendar_date of Time dimension table (Day grain).

PhysicalColumn.name: Order_Day_Dt
PhysicalColumn.Description: Order Day Date: Stores the information in date format.

PhysicalColumn.name: Prod_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Product Key: Joins to Prod_Key of Products dimension table.

PhysicalColumn.name: Empl_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Employee Key: Joins to Empl_Key column of Employees dimension table.

PhysicalColumn.name: Units
PhysicalColumn.Description: Units: Stores units information as an integer.

PhysicalColumn.name: Bill_Mth_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Bill Month Key: Joins to Mth_Key of Time dimension table (Mth grain).

PhysicalColumn.name: Paid_Day_Dt
PhysicalColumn.Description: Paid Day Date: Stores the information in date format.

PhysicalColumn.name: Currency
PhysicalColumn.Description: Currency: Stores currency information like AUD, USD, EUR..

PhysicalColumn.name: Discnt_Value
PhysicalColumn.Description: Discount Value: Stores discount value as a double.

PhysicalColumn.name: Shipto_Addr_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Shipto Address Key: Joins to Address_Key column of Addresses dimension table.

PhysicalColumn.name: Discnt_Rate
PhysicalColumn.Description: Discount Rate: Stores discount rate as an integer.

PhysicalColumn.name: Office_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Office Key: Joins to Office_Key of Employees dimension table.

PhysicalColumn.name: Order_Status
PhysicalColumn.Description: Order Status: Stores order status values like '1-Booked','2-Fulfilled' and so on.

PhysicalColumn.name: Order_Type
PhysicalColumn.Description: Order Type:Stores order type value like 'Secure','Express' and so on.

PhysicalColumn.name: Cost_Variable
PhysicalColumn.Description: Revenue: Stores revenue information as a double.

PhysicalColumn.name: Cost_Fixed
PhysicalColumn.Description: Revenue: Stores revenue information as a double.

PhysicalColumn.name: ORDER_DTIME1_DB_TZ
PhysicalColumn.Description: Order Day Date: Stores the information in Timestamp format.
